summaries.short: Jeanie Finlay spent a year on the set of “Game of Thrones” chronicling the creation of the show’s last season.
summaries.full: For a year, filmmaker Jeanie Finlay was embedded on the set of “Game of Thrones,” chronicling the creation of the show’s most ambitious and complicated season. The result is this film which provides an intimate portrait from the trenches of production, following the crew and the cast as they contend with extreme weather, punishing deadlines and a fandom hungry for spoilers.
